LucasArts Insider
The Official LucasArts.com Newsletter
Issue #29 - January 16, 2003
http://www.lucasarts.com


In this issue:

- Indy: Must-have title of 2003!
- RTX Red Rock Cutscene Debut
- Gladius Official Site Update 
- Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic
- Current Titles In Stores Now
- Star Wars Galaxies: April 15 Release Date
- Company Store Indy Special 


~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Indiana Jones® - Must Have Title of 2003
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Discover why Official Xbox(TM) Magazine called Indiana Jones and the 
Emperor's Tomb(TM) "the first must-have title of 2003." Visit the
official site where you will find previews, an action-packed game
trailer and the first PlayStation®2 screenshots available! 

   http://www.emperorstomb.com


~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
RTX Red Rock(TM) - Cutscene Debut
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
What is RTX and how did Wheeler get chosen to save the universe? Find
out in the opening cutscene debut coming soon to the official site!
While you're waiting for this exciting cinematic feature, download new
RTX Red Rock wallpaper to your desktop, view more concept art in the
gallery and check out brand new screenshots from the game. 

   http://www.rtxredrock.com


~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Gladius(TM) Official Site Update 
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Explore the recently updated Gladius official site for further story
information in the second entry of The Lost Scrolls, a new arena in the
Map Tour and additional weapon descriptions in the Gameplay section. 

   http://www.gladius.com


~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Star Wars®: Knights of the Old Republic(TM) Features
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Learn more about locations like the familiar desert land of Tatooine or
the Wookiee home of Kashyyyk in the Worlds section of the official site
for Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic. 

   http://www.swkotor.com


~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Now Available from LucasArts
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Play the role of the dangerous Jango Fett in Star Wars Bounty 
Hunter(TM) for PlayStation 2 and GameCube(TM), lead epic battles in 
Star Wars: The Clone Wars(TM) for PlayStation 2 and GameCube, and tap 
into the powers of the Force as Kyle Katarn in Jedi Outcast(TM) for PC,
Xbox and GameCube. 

   http://www.starwarsbountyhunter.com
   http://www.swclonewars.com
   http://www.jedioutcast.com


~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Star Wars Galaxies(TM) - April 15 Release 
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
LucasArts and Sony Online Entertainment announced April 15, 2003 as
the confirmed release date for Star Wars Galaxies. Celebrate with
new wallpapers featuring a Wookiee warrior, an elusive Jedi Knight,
a cunning bounty hunter or Darth Vader himself in the product site
gallery. 

   http://www.lucasarts.com/products/galaxies


~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Company Store - Indy Special
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Pre-order your copy of Indiana Jones and the Emperor's Tomb for Xbox or
PC from the LucasArts Company Store and get free shipping and handling
plus a collectible light-up spiral pen featuring the game logo with 
your order! 

   http://store.lucasarts.com


